---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Sunny Dray's Cleaning | About"
  description="About page description for search results."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="wrapper py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">
      A clean home can make everything feel more manageable. We’re here to help
      you reset.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
      <div
        class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border p-6 md:p-8"
        style="border-color: var(--border);"
      >
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">How we help</h2>

        <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Sunny Dray’s Cleaning was created with one simple belief: a clean
          space can make everything feel more manageable.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">
          When your home feels overwhelming, it’s hard to know where to begin.
          Having someone step in, reset the space, and give you a true clean
          slate can make a real difference. Whether it’s a one-time deep clean
          or a recurring service, our goal is to take that burden off your
          shoulders.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">
          We approach every home with care, attention to detail, and respect for
          your time and space. From the first visit to ongoing cleanings, we’re
          here to help you feel more comfortable, more organized, and more at
          ease in your home.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Because sometimes, the biggest relief starts with a clean space.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <a
            href="/intake"
            data-astro-reload="true"
            class="rounded-xl bg-[#d93a1b] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-[#F29710] inline-flex"
          >
            Get Relief
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="mt-8 about-div rounded-3xl text-center"
        style="border-color: var(--border);"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/IMG_5579.png"
          alt="Owner of Sunny Dray's Cleaning"
          class="max-w-sm h-101.25 rounded-3xl object-contain"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm px-4" style="color: var(--muted);">
          Owner-operated by Andraya, locally based in Southern New Hampshire.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
